Package: TuNeS
Title: Tumor Nest Selector - Spatial Analysis of Tumor Boundaries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("TuNeS", "Developer", email = "noah.simons@providence.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive tool for selecting tumor regions in spatial transcriptomics data
    and analyzing genomic separation at varying distances from tumor boundaries. Provides
    a Shiny interface for drawing polygons and functions for calculating distance-based
    metrics including transcriptomic distance, differential expression strength, and
    cell type composition differences.
